Name: REBCO
Sentence: Rare-earth-based cuprate superconductor REBa 2 Cu 3 O y (REBCO, RE = rare earth elements or Y) coated conductors are promising conductors for various kinds of electric power applications owing to their high critical temperature (T c ) of over 90 K and large critical current density (J c ) in high magnetic fields .
